import React from 'react' import { UilArrowDown, UilArrowUp, UilSun, UilWind, UilTear, UilSunset, UilTemperature, } from "@iconscout/react-unicons"; import { formatToLocalTime, iconURLFromCode } from '../services/weatherService'; function TempDetails({weather: { details, icon, temp, temp_min, temp_max, sunrise, sunset, speed, humidity, feels_like, timezone }}) { return (

{details}

{`${temp.toFixed()}°`}

Feels like: {`${feels_like.toFixed()}°`}
Humidity: {`${humidity.toFixed()}%`}
Wind: {`${speed.toFixed()} km/h`}

Rise: {formatToLocalTime(sunrise,timezone, "hh:mm a")}

|

Set: {formatToLocalTime(sunset,timezone, "hh:mm a")}

|

High: {`${temp_max.toFixed()}°`}

|

Low: {`${temp_max.toFixed()}°`}

) } export default TempDetails
